comment: LHH shows Walker (CHA) put his hand under the ball and bring it to a pause.
[Observable in enhanced video] LHH shows Lamb (CHA) lift his pivot foot before releasing the ball to start his dribble.
Lamb (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on Powell (DAL) during Gibson's (DAL) drive to the basket. Powell then dislodges Lamb from his rebounding position.
Batum (CHA) maintains a legal guarding position on Matthews (DAL) and does not affect his FOM away from the ball.
[Observable in enhanced video] Gibson (DAL) slides his pivot foot before releasing the ball.
Mejri (DAL) sets the screen on Walker (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Matthews (DAL) and Zeller (CHA) make incidental contact away from the play.
Finney-Smith (DAL) maintains legal guarding position on Lamb (CHA) and does not affect his SQBR.
Mejri (DAL) commits a take foul on Kidd-Gilchrist (CHA).
Barnes (DAL) and Walker (CHA) make incidental contact during the rebound.
Gibson (DAL) commits a take foul on Batum (CHA).
